<paragraph id="IAS01_41" base="F3903234" principles="yes"><paranum>41</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IASÂ 1"/><data name="paranum" value="41"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS01_P0221">If an entity changes the presentation or classification of items in its <xref base="F3902997" href="IAS01_7.dita#IAS01_7/IAS01_P0013">financial statements<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0146"/></ph></xref>, it shall reclassify comparative amounts unless reclassification is <xref base="F5148372" href="IAS01_7.dita#IAS01_7/IAS01_P0017">impracticable<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0177"/></ph></xref>. When an entity reclassifies comparative amounts, it shall disclose (including as at the beginning of the preceding period):</p><ol id="IAS01_L0022" base="F3903236" type="lower-alpha"><li id="IAS01_41_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IAS01_P0222" base="F3903237">the nature of the reclassification;</p></li><li id="IAS01_41_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IAS01_P0223" base="F3903239">the amount of each item or class of items that is reclassified; and</p></li><li id="IAS01_41_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p id="IAS01_P0224" base="F3903241">the reason for the reclassification.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>